name: Plane Window #1
description:
I get excited every time I´m in a plane window
like a kid, I love to see the world from above

Planes are vehicles for ideas
We carry with them, planes carry with us

We see the world from another point of view
and
We have big joy because we are going to landing in somewhere else.

That time I was going to Italy
I felt grateful of seeing the sunrise from there.
